/**
 * The Void — Game Engine
 *
 * Core game logic for The Void cosmogenesis teaching game.
 * Every mechanic is governed by the God Formula: w = R - min(v, R) + 1
 *
 * The engine is pure logic — no rendering, no IO, no side effects.
 * Given a state and an action, it returns a new state and events.
 *
 * Key design constraints:
 * - Failure is the survival resource (buleyean RL)
 * - No player dominance (BFT-guaranteed)
 * - Monte Carlo encounters (non-deterministic but fair)
 * - Self-optimizing balance via gnosis
 * - Time is gnosis time (picolorenzos)
 *
 * @module @a0n/gnosis/void-game-engine
 */

